  <description type="morphology">Spikelets ascending-erect, forming less than 40° angle with rachis, closely spaced (2 or more per mm of rachis), 15–25(–55) mm; floral scales deltate-ovate, widest at 1/4–1/3 length, 2.4–2.6 × 1.7–1.8 mm. Flowers: anthers 1.2 mm; styles 0.9 mm; stigmas 1.6 mm.</description>
